210812.title: Front Street East and Yonge Street.
210812.text:
[ca. 1880]
Description: 1 photonegative : glass, b&w; ; 10 x13 cm
Citation: Fonds 1257, Series 1057, Item 12
Condition: Vinegar syndrome has affected the original film media. It has been frozen for preservation reasons, and therefore may not be requested for viewing in the Research Hall. 
Copyright: Copyright was transferred to the City of Toronto by the copyright owner. ...more
Scope: Item is an image of Front Street East from east of Yonge Street showing a horse-drawn cart in front of Stark & Bruce Importers.
